     fhir:Narrative.div "<div xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\"><p class=\"res-header-id\"><b>Generated Narrative: ValueSet ManglendeEORTC</b></p><a name=\"ManglendeEORTC\"> </a><a name=\"hcManglendeEORTC\"> </a><p>This value set includes codes based on the following rules:</p><ul><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-TreatmentNotGiven.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/TreatmentNotGiven</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-TreatmentNotGiven.html#TreatmentNotGiven-bad_condition\">bad_condition</a></td><td>For dårlig</td><td>Bad condition / For dårlig</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-TreatmentNotGiven.html#TreatmentNotGiven-unwanted\">unwanted</a></td><td>Afslog</td><td>Unwanted treatment / Ønskede ikke behandling</td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-TreatmentNotGiven.html#TreatmentNotGiven-died\">died</a></td><td>Ikke i live</td><td>Died before treatment / Døde før behandling</td></tr></table></li><li>Include these codes as defined in <a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html\"><code>https://kip.rkkp.dk/fhir/CodeSystem/GenericValues</code></a><span title=\"Version is not explicitly stated, which means it is fixed to the version provided in this specification\"> version ?2.23.1</span><table class=\"none\"><tr><td style=\"white-space:nowrap\"><b>Code</b></td><td><b>Display</b></td><td><b>Definition</b></td></tr><tr><td><a href=\"CodeSystem-GenericValues.html#GenericValues-none\">none</a></td><td>Ikke begrundet</td><td>None - used to choose none of the available values</td></tr></table></li></ul></div>"
